data.description: Discover this spacious, well-located home with stunning Wasatch Front views and nearby playgrounds. Enjoy an inviting and cozy atmosphere with a fireplace, vaulted ceilings, and a versatile den/playroom. The second level features four bedrooms, including a master with dual closets, and a luxurious master bath offer ample comfort. Recent upgrades feature new flooring and carpet. The fully finished basement with 10-foot ceilings and a walk-out design adds valuable living space, a fifth bedroom and another full bath. Practical amenities include a three-car garage, RV parking, and a generously sized driveway wide enough for four vehicles. Community perks come with an HOA covering a clubhouse and pool. Act quickly  this gem won't last! Square footage is estimated; buyer verification recommended.
